Type Byte be u8.

Type Word be u16.

Enum Mode backed by Byte has idle be 0; active be 1.

Packed layout record Header has mode: Mode; length: Word.

To main, giving i32.
Let bytes be array of 3 Byte containing 1, 42, 0.
Let header be read Header from bytes at 0.
Give header.length as i32 when header.mode is equal to Mode.active; otherwise 0.
